ld_slug','construction-installation'),(548,105,'_wp_trash_meta_status','publish'),(549,105,'_wp_trash_meta_time','1425067525'),(550,99,'_wp_old_slug','design-engineering'),(559,117,'_edit_last','1'),(560,117,'_edit_lock','1425079728:1'),(561,117,'_wp_trash_meta_status','draft'),(562,117,'_wp_trash_meta_time','1425081277'),(563,118,'_edit_last','1'),(565,118,'_wpcf-about-us-content-sort-order','a:1:{i:0;i:578;}'),(567,118,'_wpcf-about-us-content-list-sort-order','a:1:{i:0;i:579;}'),(574,118,'_wpcf-certification-list-sort-order','a:6:{i:0;i:580;i:1;i:581;i:2;i:582;i:3;i:583;i:4;i:584;i:5;i:585;}'),(575,118,'_edit_lock','1425083040:1'),(576,118,'_wp_old_slug','118'),(577,118,'wpcf-about-us-right-content','Founded in 2002, Red Wave Communications Inc. has grown into a leading low voltage contractor throughout California, offering more than 30 years of combined experience and expertise in integration. Red Wave Communications is licensed by the California Contractors State License Board with A, B, C-7, and C-10 classifications. In addition, we are a State of California DVBE & SBE organization, certified by the Department of General Services.'),(578,118,'wpcf-about-us-content','Through a culture of continuous improvement, Red Wave designs, builds, and maintains a variety of high quality low voltage systems, including, but not limited to, access control, audio/visual, automation, life safety, security, and structured cabling.\r\n\r\nWe are trusted system integrators providing easy technology solutions for businesses and homes.\r\n\r\nWe are on our way to becoming the premier system integration partner throughout California.\r\n\r\nRed Wave Communications provides a single point contact for design and installation of high quality low voltage systems. Specializing in system integration and security, we adhere to the highest quality standards to ensure customer satisfaction. As a full service company, we offer AUTOCAD design including the ability to perform 3D rendering. With a bonding capacity for large projects, low EMR, IIPP, and safety plans in place, Red Wave Communications is capable of handling all your residential and business design and integration needs with helpful and convenient customer service.'),(579,118,'wpcf-about-us-content-list',''),(580,118,'wpcf-certification-list','<b>Small Business</b>\r\nThis certification promotes Californias small business, and encourages sustained economic prosperity through working together to maintain the strength of small businesses throughout California.'),(581,118,'wpcf-certification-list','<b>NICET</b>\r\nThe National Institute for Certification in Engineering Technologies was created by the National Society of Professional Engineers to serve the certification needs of the engineering technology community.\r\n'),(582,118,'wpcf-certification-list','<b>BICSI</b>\r\n<i>The Building Industry Consulting Service International</i> is a credential and assurance that an individual has knowledge in a designated area of information technology, systems design, or installation.\r\n'),(583,118,'wpcf-certification-list','<b>RCDD</b>\r\nRegistered Communications Distribution Designer demonstrated their knowledge in the design, implementation and integration of information technology, and related infrastructure.\r\n'),(584,118,'wpcf-certification-list','<b>NFPA</b>\r\nNational Fire Protection Association provides codes, standards, research, training, and education for all of its members in public safety and fire safety.\r\n'),(585,118,'wpcf-certification-list','<b>BSIS</b>\r\nBureau of Security and Investigated Service registers certified, professional security guards in the state of California.\r\n'),(586,120,'_edit_last','1'),(587,120,'_edit_lock','1425332739:1'),(588,120,'wpcf-system-name','Systems'),(589,120,'wpcf-system-description','We are partnered with leading technology manufacturers to customize the right solution.'),(590,120,'wpcf-system-list',''),(591,120,'_wpcf-system-list-sort-order','a:1:{i